In addition to this we continue to catalog out many hundreds of thousands of micromagnetic solutions for different minerals and particle geometries and will make this database available on our University servers as a resource to the palaomagnetic and rock magnetic community. From this database they can interrogate the magnetic recording fidelity of a wide selection of paleomagnetic particles. 
